<br>
Somehow a good number of people here want wizards to be more group friendly without getting any kind of group friendly buff.  I've tried to think about what I would add along those lines if I could, but I can't think of much.<br>
<br>
Granted I'm not complaining, cause I think wizards do good in groups.  I just think there's something that we could get that would offer more to a group, and personally I'd like to see some group buffs. <p><table width="320" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
